title: Witness tells Cosby, 'You know what you did!'
text:
Witness tells Cosby, 'You know what you did!' 11:03am IST - 01:40 
The judge in Bill Cosby’s sexual assault trial refused to declare a mistrial on Wednesday after one of the accusers called as a prosecution witness blurted out from the witness stand, 'You know what you did, don’t you, Mr. Cosby?' Lisa Bernhard reports.
